SolusVMController is a PHP application to manage all your SolusVM based VMs under single interface.
This application access your VPS using API provided by Soluslabs. Please make sure API access
has been enabled for your VPS provider in order to use this application.

Program features:

- Add multiple VMs
- Boot, reboot, and shutdown your VMs from one interface
- Tag to organize VMs
- Multiple users supported


For bugs report or suggestions, please e-mail support[at]solusvmcontroller.com
Twitter: http://twitter.com/svmcontroller